title: Donaire vs Gaballo HIGHLIGHTS: December 11, 2021 | PBC on SHOWTIME
author: Premier Boxing Champions
description:
Nonito Donaire proved he's still got it at the age of 39, scoring a fourth-round body shot knockout over formerly unbeaten Reymart Gaballo in their WBC World Super Bantamweight Championship, live on SHOWTIME from Dignity Health Sports Park in Carson, California. Donaire improves to 42-6 (28 KOs).
